1187
01:21:41,482 --> 01:21:42,900
Hey, we're gonna beat them, John.

1188
01:21:42,983 --> 01:21:44,651
- Me and you, together. Okay?
- Thanks, Roger.

1189
01:21:44,735 --> 01:21:46,236
Sure, man. I'll see you.

1190
01:21:46,320 --> 01:21:48,989
