01:27:39,172 --> 01:27:42,509
<i>To make you stay away so long?</i>

1290
01:27:42,843 --> 01:27:45,929
<i>Baby love, my baby love.</i>

1291
01:27:46,138 --> 01:27:50,600
<i>Been missing ya, oh, miss kissing ya</i>

