01:33:00,744 --> 01:33:04,456
about the fine fighting spirit
your men have here, too.

1365
01:33:04,831 --> 01:33:06,166
(CHUCKLING)

1366
01:33:07,792 --> 01:33:11,671
Wait a minute, Major.
